sequenceDiagram
    participant 👤 User
    participant 🎯 Notely
    participant 🎤 ASR
    participant 👁️ OCR
    participant 🤖 Enhancer

    👤 User->>🎯 Notely: Initialize with API key
    👤 User->>🎯 Notely: process(video_path)

    🎯 Notely->>🎯 Notely: Extract audio & frames

    🎯 Notely->>🎤 ASR: Transcribe audio
    🎤 ASR-->>🎯 Notely: Transcript with timestamps

    🎯 Notely->>👁️ OCR: Recognize text from frames
    👁️ OCR-->>🎯 Notely: Extracted text

    🎯 Notely->>🤖 Enhancer: Semantic chunking (2000/1000)
    🤖 Enhancer->>🤖 Enhancer: Layer 1: Comprehension
    Note over 🤖 Enhancer: Extract semantic info<br/>Min 300 words/chunk

    🤖 Enhancer->>🤖 Enhancer: Layer 2: Structuring
    Note over 🤖 Enhancer: Organize by topic<br/>Min 200 words/section

    🤖 Enhancer-->>🎯 Notely: Structured content

    🎯 Notely->>🎯 Notely: Format & beautify (LaTeX support)
    🎯 Notely-->>👤 User: NotelyResult

    👤 User->>🎯 Notely: result.save("notes.md")
    🎯 Notely-->>👤 User: ✅ Saved
